description: The Cloud Ninja skill is your guide to Amazon Web Services.  It will keep you up to date on announcements from AWS (What's New!), tell you more about individual AWS services (Tell me about AWS Lambda), and will accept your feedback and suggestions on what things you think should be added to the skill (Learn something new).
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Cloud Ninja What's New
Tell me more about Amazon S3
Learn to tell me what alarms need attention
name: Ask Cloud Ninja
shortDescription: The Cloud Ninja is your guide to Amazon Web Services, including helping you keep up to date with recent AWS news.
